01:11:08,883 --> 01:11:10,544
Thank you, Jeffrey.

943
01:11:17,758 --> 01:11:18,773
- Cole.
- Yeah.

944
01:11:18,773 --> 01:11:19,807
 Your boy's back.

945
01:11:23,831 --> 01:11:25,389
That's him, right?
